<title>Configure K8s Ingress Nginx</title><link>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/configure-k8s-ingress-nginx/</link><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jun 2022 19:44:54 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/configure-k8s-ingress-nginx/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Hugo 内置的 Chroma 语法高亮</title><link>https://erge.blog/post/syntax-highlighting.html</link><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jun 2022 19:09:52 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://erge.blog/post/syntax-highlighting.html</guid><description>&lt;p>Hugo 通过 Chroma 提供非常快速的语法高亮显示，现 Hugo 中使用 Chroma 作为代码块高亮支持，它内置在 Go 语言当中，速度是真的非常、非常快，而且最为重要的是它也兼容之前我们使用的 Pygments 方式。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>以下通过 Hugo 内置短代码 &lt;code>highlight&lt;/code> 和 &lt;code>Markdown&lt;/code> 代码块方式分别验证不同语言的代码块渲染效果并能正确高亮显示，有关优化语法突出显示的更多信息，请参阅
&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/configuration-markup#highlight" title="Hugo 文档" rel="noopener external nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank" class=" exturl">
Hugo 文档
&lt;i class="fa fa-external-link-alt">&lt;/i>
&lt;/a>。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Configure K8s Project</title><link>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/configure-k8s-project/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jun 2022 21:23:10 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/configure-k8s-project/</guid><description/></item><item><title>支持 Emoji 表情</title><link>https://erge.blog/post/emoji-support.html</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Jun 2022 19:46:45 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://erge.blog/post/emoji-support.html</guid><description>&lt;p>Emoji 可以通过多种方式在 Hugo 项目中启用。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>
&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/functions/emojify/" title="&amp;lt;code&amp;gt;emojify&amp;lt;/code&amp;gt;" rel="noopener external nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank" class=" exturl">
&lt;code>emojify&lt;/code>
&lt;i class="fa fa-external-link-alt">&lt;/i>
&lt;/a> 方法可以直接在模板中调用, 或者使用
&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/templates/shortcode-templates#inline-shortcodes" title="行内 Shortcodes" rel="noopener external nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank" class=" exturl">
行内 Shortcodes
&lt;i class="fa fa-external-link-alt">&lt;/i>
&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>要全局使用 emoji, 需要在你的
&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/configuration/" title="网站配置" rel="noopener external nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank" class=" exturl">
网站配置
&lt;i class="fa fa-external-link-alt">&lt;/i>
&lt;/a>中设置 &lt;code>enableEmoji&lt;/code> 为 &lt;code>true&lt;/code>，
然后你就可以直接在文章中输入 emoji 的代码。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Markdown 语法支持</title><link>https://erge.blog/post/markdown-syntax.html</link><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jun 2022 11:52:18 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://erge.blog/post/markdown-syntax.html</guid><description>&lt;p>仅以此篇文章来测试下在 &lt;code>NexT&lt;/code> 主题中在通过 &lt;code>Hugo&lt;/code> 引擎来建站时，是否支持 &lt;code>Markdown&lt;/code> 文件内容中所写的各种语法，并展示下实际的效果。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Install Kubernetes Cluster</title><link>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/install-kubernetes-cluster/</link><pubDate>Mon, 30 May 2022 19:12:46 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/install-kubernetes-cluster/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Configure K8s Auth</title><link>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/configure-k8s-auth/</link><pubDate>Mon, 30 May 2022 17:46:41 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/configure-k8s-auth/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Configure K8s Helm</title><link>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/configure-k8s-helm/</link><pubDate>Sun, 29 May 2022 19:31:37 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/configure-k8s-helm/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Configure K8s Data Storage</title><link>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/configure-k8s-data-storage/</link><pubDate>Sun, 29 May 2022 19:09:13 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/configure-k8s-data-storage/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Configure K8s Service</title><link>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/configure-k8s-service/</link><pubDate>Fri, 27 May 2022 22:01:33 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/configure-k8s-service/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Configure K8s Kind</title><link>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/configure-k8s-kind/</link><pubDate>Fri, 27 May 2022 20:54:44 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://erge.blog/linux/kubernetes/configure-k8s-kind/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Install Logs Finder</title><link>https:/